Ibubeleye Whyte (amụrụ na 9 Jenụwarị 1992 na Enugu, Naijiria) bụ onye na-agba bọọlụ Naijiria nke na-agbachitere ndị na-agba ọsọ ugbu a ma na-agba egwu ugbu a maka Rivers Angels na Njikọ Ụmụ nwanyị Naijiria na otu egwuregwu bọọlụ ụmụ nwanyị Naijịria.
Whyte mere nke mbụ ya na mba ụwa na 2012 FIFA U-20 Women's World Cup na mmeri 2-1 na Japan U-20. Ọ bụkwa otu n'ime ndị okenye na African Women's Championship nke 2012 na ndị mmẹri nke 2014
N'ọnwa Mee afọ 2015, a kpọrọ ya ka ọ bụrụ otu n'ime ndị otụ Naịjirịa na 2015 FIFA Women's World Cup
